𝘚𝘶𝘱𝘦𝘳 𝘔𝘢𝘳𝘪𝘰 𝘎𝘢𝘭𝘢𝘹𝘺 2 continues to go incredibly hard.

It’s simpler than the first game in its story
and many of its mechanics, but ultimately
it’s more 𝘚𝘶𝘱𝘦𝘳 𝘔𝘢𝘳𝘪𝘰 𝘎𝘢𝘭𝘢𝘹𝘺, and that’s a very good thing.

It inherits most of its predecessor’s greatest strengths,
including stellar environments,
out-of-this-world gameplay,
and a breathtaking score.


































































because you can’t breathe in space
